About Me

Welcome to my Bulk card pricing tool! My background is in Data Engineering/Software Engineering work. I had a lot of cards I wanted to look up and the tools and APIs currently available were lackluster at best. There wasn't an easy way to get to the exact card pages I wanted without clicking on hundreds of links, so I decided to create my own. In that process I figured some of my friends might want to use it too so I created a front end for the project.

My Journey

I've worked with Python for about 4 years now and I have been recently working on React/TypeScript projects.

Technologies Used

  • React with TypeScript for frontend development.
  • FastAPI for backend API development.
  • Requests and BeautifulSoup for web scraping.
  • Papa Parse for CSV data handling in the browser.

What This Project Offers

This project allows users to import CSV data, manage their cards, perform data validation, and get pricing information by grade. It includes features for tracking holo, reverse holo, first edition, and limited edition cards, ensuring accurate card information is pulled.

Feel free to explore the app and upload your own card collections. Thank you for stopping by!
